text: Maksim Shishlov (; ; born 17 February 1996) is a Belarusian professional footballer. As of 2020, he plays for Slonim-2017 on loan from Neman Grodno.Player's profile at pressball.by ==References== == External links == * * Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Belarusian footballers Category:Association football goalkeepers Category:FC Neman Grodno players Category:FC Granit Mikashevichi players Category:FC Belshina Bobruisk players Category:FC Slonim-2017 players
